201.DESCRIPTION: Success - OK - but not final response

206.DESCRIPTION: Partial Success but not desired result, considered failed

400.DESCRIPTION: Unexpected input, processed to not accessible elements

401.DESCRIPTION: Unexpected input, unauthorized or invalid login

403.DESCRIPTION: Unexpected input, unauthorized, valid login but not allowed to access

404.DESCRIPTION: Unexpected input, no resource found to process

406.DESCRIPTION: Unexpected input, not clear to process

409.DESCRIPTION: Unexpected input, not clear to process

422.DESCRIPTION: Wrong input format in request, no processing of request
